<p class="indent1" style="-uslm-lc:I12" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">For purposes of determining the balances of the Highway Trust Fund and the Mass Transit Account after <date date="1998-09-30">September 30, 1998</date>, the opening balance of the Highway Trust Fund (other than the Mass Transit Account) on <date date="1998-10-01">October 1, 1998</date>, shall be $8,000,000,000. The Secretary shall cancel obligations held by the Highway Trust Fund to reflect the reduction in the balance under this paragraph.</p>
